---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Broadway Pizza — 55 years in Nedlands. Perth's original pizza legend since 1969.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="tagline-sm">Since 1969</p>
      <h1>A Slice of Perth History</h1>
      <p>165 Broadway, Nedlands — still going strong after all these years.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story">
    <div class="container story-grid">
      <div class="story-image">
        <div class="pizza-emoji">🍕</div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2>From Al's to Broadway</h2>
        <p>It started as Al's Pizza in 1969 — a humble little shop on Broadway with a brick oven and a simple idea: make really good pizza, charge fair prices, treat people like neighbours.</p>
        <p>Five and a half decades later, the name changed to Broadway Pizza, the oven got an upgrade, and the suburb around us has grown and changed — but the pizza? Same recipe. Same commitment to quality. Same Nedlands institution.</p>
        <p>We've fed generations of families, late-night uni students, sports teams after the game, couples on date night, and locals who just want a reliable, great-tasting pizza. That's what we do.</p>
        <p>We're not the fanciest pizza in Perth. We're not trying to be. We're the pizza that's been here, that will be here, and that you can always count on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🔥</div>
          <h3>Fresh, Not Fancy</h3>
          <p>Made to order, every time. We don't do pre-made, we don't do shortcuts. Your pizza is made when you call.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">💚</div>
          <h3>Family & Locals First</h3>
          <p>We're not a chain. We're a neighbourhood shop. When you walk in, we know you. When you call, we pick up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">💯</div>
          <h3>Value You Can Count On</h3>
          <p>55 years of fair pricing. Great pizza doesn't have to cost a fortune. Our sizes actually feed people.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Consistency</h3>
          <p>The pizza you had five years ago? It'll be the same today. That's not an accident — it's a promise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="facts">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="facts-grid">
        <div class="fact">
          <div class="fact-num">55+</div>
          <div class="fact-label">Years in Nedlands</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <div class="fact-num">11</div>
          <div class="fact-label">Delivery Suburbs</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <div class="fact-num">1969</div>
          <div class="fact-label">Year Founded</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <div class="fact-num">∞</div>
          <div class="fact-label">Satisfied Customers</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="visit-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Come Say Hello</h2>
      <p>We're in the Broadway Fair Shopping Centre, right on Broadway. Easy parking, easy find.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get Directions & Hours →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.page-header { background: var(--warm); padding: 4rem 0 3rem; text-align: center; }
.page-header .tagline-sm { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.page-header h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.page-header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }

.container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

.story { padding: 5rem 0; }
.story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .story-image { display: none; } }
.story-image { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.pizza-emoji { font-size: 10rem; opacity: 0.15; }
.story-text h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.story-text p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

.values { background: var(--cream); padding: 5rem 0; }
.values h2 { font-size: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
.value-card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
.value-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.value-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--charcoal); }
.value-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; }

.facts { padding: 4rem 0; }
.facts-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .facts-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
.fact { text-align: center; background: var(--charcoal); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
.fact-num { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--warm); line-height: 1; }
.fact-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

.visit-cta { padding: 5rem 0; text-align: center; background: var(--cream); }
.visit-cta h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.visit-cta p { color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>